caption.body: Join us at the Aviation Museum and Library on Friday, November 3, 2023 at 5:30 PM! The San Francisco Aeronautical Society and The Pan Am Historical Foundation will present “Pan Am on Film” featuring rare screenings from the Pan American World Airways Archival Film Library. Join special guests Edward S. Trippe, the current chairman of the Pan Am Historical Foundation along with John L. Martin, the current president of the San Francisco Aeronautical Society and former director of San Francisco International Airport and John H. Hill, the former Assistant Director of SFO Museum.  RSVP for this FREE event at https://sfaero.org/event/movie-night-at-sfo-pan-am-on-film/
